OL,3,CPost Office boss 'exonerated of
OL,4,Cmisconduct claims' after bullying
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,Fchief executive Nick Read has been
OL,8,F"exonerated of all misconduct
OL,9,Fallegations" after the former chairman
OL,10,Fof the troubled company claimed Mr
OL,11,FRead was prioritising his salary over
OL,12,Ftackling a culture of toxicity.
OL,14,FThe external report, which the Post
OL,15,FOffice has not released, was said by
OL,16,Fformer chairman Henry Staunton to
OL,17,Fcontain allegations about Mr Read's
OL,18,F"conduct and lack of his management of
OL,19,Fthe many governance and compliance
OL,20,Fissues".
