OL,7,FMr Staunton previously told the
OL,8,FBusiness and Trade Committee that
OL,9,Fthere was an attitude from "Read and
OL,10,Fhis henchmen" towards the company's
OL,11,Fformer HR director as a "pain in the
OL,12,Farse for focusing on tackling the
OL,13,Ftoxic culture rather than prioritising
OL,14,FRead's salary".
OL,16,FHe said the document, which he
OL,17,Freferred to during his evidence to MPs
OL,18,Fin February, included Mr Read's
OL,19,F"badgering over his salary and
OL,20,Frepeated threats to resign".
