OL,3,CPost Office boss 'exonerated of
OL,4,Cmisconduct claims' after bullying
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FThe Post Office said Mr Staunton's
OL,8,Fclaims contained "inaccuracies and
OL,9,Ffalsehoods" and Mr Read told his staff
OL,10,Flast month that he "absolutely
OL,11,Frefutes" bullying claims.
OL,13,FOn Wednesday, the organisation said
OL,14,Fthe report, compiled by barrister
OL,15,FMarianne Tutin of Devereux Chambers,
OL,16,Fhad exonerated Mr Read of all
OL,17,Fmisconduct allegations and he had the
OL,18,F"united backing of the board".
