OL,7,FA spokesman for the Department of
OL,8,FBusiness and Trade (DBT) said Mr Read
OL,9,Fhas "the confidence of the Government".
OL,11,FIn a statement, the Post Office said:
OL,12,F"Over the last few months an
OL,13,Findependent barrister has been
OL,14,Finvestigating a Speak Up complaint
OL,15,Finto various allegations, which
OL,16,Fincluded a number of misconduct
OL,17,Fallegations against our CEO, Nick Read.
