OL,4,Cmisconduct claims' after bullying
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"Following several interviews and
OL,8,Fexamination of documents by the
OL,9,Fbarrister, Nick has been exonerated of
OL,10,Fall the misconduct allegations and has
OL,11,Fthe full and united backing of the
OL,12,FBoard to continue to lead the business.
OL,14,F"The Board regards the Speak Up
OL,15,Fprocess as critical to the open and
OL,16,Fsupportive culture it wants to
OL,17,Fencourage at the Post Office.
