OL,3,CPost Office boss 'exonerated of
OL,4,Cmisconduct claims' after bullying
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"The integrity of that Speak Up
OL,8,Fprocess relies on confidentiality for
OL,9,Fwhistleblowers and therefore we will
OL,10,Fnot be providing further detail on
OL,11,Fthis or any other Speak Up
OL,12,Finvestigation.
OL,14,F"It is unacceptable that this specific
OL,15,Fprocess was referred to in the public
OL,16,Fdomain but notwithstanding that, Post
OL,17,FOffice wants to make clear that Speak
OL,18,FUp allegations will always be
OL,19,Fthoroughly and consistently
OL,20,Finvestigated, whoever they are aimed
OL,21,Fat."
