OL,7,FThe Post Office said the external
OL,8,Finvestigator has made recommendations
OL,9,Fon improvements that can be made to
OL,10,Fthe company's processes.
OL,12,FThe statement added: "Those
OL,13,Frecommendations are helpful and we
OL,14,Fwill ensure that they are properly and
OL,15,Fpromptly addressed going forward."
